的环境，既不影响厕所的功能性使用和趣味性体验，也更好保护游客隐私。” “开放式”厕所是否确实存在？景区是否有靠网红厕所博眼球之嫌？接受多家媒体采访时，该景区工作人员表示厕所确实存在，但是很少有人去上，并表示公司并不是以此博眼球，也不清楚设计师的初衷，但会向领导反应情况。 10月12日下午，封面新闻记者致电该景区，工作人员称：“我不清楚，也不方便透露任何情况。” （来源 封面新闻） （编辑 熊子文 刘梦鸽） 景区现开放式厕所无任何遮挡物"},"attached_info":"Cj8IwJfsqKyt5ccoEAMaCDcxNjY2NDM3ILC+m4sGMDo4rwhACnIJNDkyMjMyODM3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"146 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-85c7820adce2a37cbec57c15128f288e_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1634437392.0567255","card_id":"Q_492817332","target":{"id":492817332,"title":"2021 KPL 秋季赛成都AG 1:3 武汉eStar Pro，如何评价这场比赛？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/492817332","type":"question","created":1634389354,"answer_count":40,"follower_count":50,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[163534,183549,185504,389491,777657],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4IwJfsqKyt5ccoEAMaCDcxNzk2Mzk5IOqaq4sGMAA4MkALcgk0OTI4MTczMzJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"108 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e0f42b402fabcaf06788879c88e5e625_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1634437392.0571485","card_id":"Q_24661754","target":{"id":24661754,"title":"《生活大爆炸》为什么没有《老友记》经典？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/24661754","type":"question","created":1406632936,"answer_count":321,"follower_count":1338,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[316,467,2211,8412,217771],"comment_count":23,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"从收视人数比较：《老友记》的收视人数在96年（约第三季）达到5300万人，《大爆炸》在第七季突破了此前了2000万收视人数。（数据来自百度百科）"},"attached_info":"Cj0IwJfsqKyt5ccoEAMaBzIwNDY